title: The Very First Night (Taylor's Version) (From The Vault)
description:
Taylor thinks about how it would be to go back to the very first night of the relationship, and relive that over and over again.. but there is some controversy over the lyrics. We discuss and dissect!

What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? There are lots of ways to reach us!
